287
00:27:05,123 --> 00:27:06,374
Okay.

288
00:27:24,059 --> 00:27:25,185
Dong-seok.

289
00:27:28,438 --> 00:27:30,148
Let's drive along the coastal road.

290
00:28:31,751 --> 00:28:35,004
I just learned that my mom
who I despise has cancer.

291
00:28:37,799 --> 00:28:39,300
And I feel weird.

292
00:28:42,053 --> 00:28:43,471
I'm neither sad…

293
00:28:45,432 --> 00:28:47,058
nor jumping

294
00:28:48,226 --> 00:28:49,811
for joy.

295
00:28:54,733 --> 00:28:56,860
The anger is slowly creeping up on me.

296
00:28:58,611 --> 00:29:00,029
I feel like shit.

297
00:29:08,580 --> 00:29:09,748
Let's go.

298
00:29:35,231 --> 00:29:36,399
Bye.

299
00:29:57,962 --> 00:29:58,797
Go home.

300
00:29:59,756 --> 00:30:00,882
Okay.

301
00:30:11,851 --> 00:30:13,561
SEON-A

302
00:30:24,697 --> 00:30:26,074
Hey, it's me.

303
00:30:27,992 --> 00:30:29,577
You finally picked up.

304
00:30:30,870 --> 00:30:34,249
I was worried you wouldn't pick up again.

305
00:30:37,126 --> 00:30:38,211
Dong-seok.

306
00:30:39,546 --> 00:30:41,047
My mom has cancer.

307
00:30:43,091 --> 00:30:44,175
It's terminal.

308
00:30:47,345 --> 00:30:48,805
But I'm fine.

309
00:30:50,390 --> 00:30:52,809
Part of me thinks
that it's finally over between us.

310
00:30:55,228 --> 00:30:56,646
I feel relieved too.

311
